# **IoT Testbed Ontology**
# ==========================

# **Introduction**
# ---------------

# This ontology defines a conceptual model for the domain of IoT testbeds, reusing existing ontologies, vocabularies, and standards whenever possible. The goal is to provide a clear and well-defined representation of IoT testbeds, their components, and their relationships.

# **Reuse Strategy**
# ------------------

# This ontology reuses the following existing ontologies, vocabularies, and standards:

# *   **Fiesta-IOT Ontology**: Reused for device and network-related concepts.
# *   **Semantic Sensor Network (SSN) Ontology**: Reused for sensor-related concepts.
# *   **Resource Description Framework (RDF) Schema**: Reused for basic data types and properties.

# **Ontology Definition**
# ----------------------

# ### Classes

# ```turtle
@prefix iota: <http://example.org/iot#> .
@prefix ssn: <http://www.w3.org/ns/ssn/> .
@prefix rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> .
@prefix rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> .
@prefix fiesta: <http://fiesta-iot.org/ontology#> .

iota:IoTTestbed a rdfs:Class ;
    rdfs:label "IoT Testbed" ;
    rdfs:comment "A testbed for IoT devices and networks." .

iota:Device a rdfs:Class ;
    rdfs:label "Device" ;
    rdfs:comment "A device in the IoT testbed." ;
    ssn:hasProperty ssn:observes .

iota:Network a rdfs:Class ;
    rdfs:label "Network" ;
    rdfs:comment "A network in the IoT testbed." ;
    ssn:hasProperty ssn:connects .

iota:Sensor a rdfs:Class ;
    rdfs:label "Sensor" ;
    rdfs:comment "A sensor in the IoT testbed." ;
    ssn:hasProperty ssn:observes .

iota:Actuator a rdfs:Class ;
    rdfs:label "Actuator" ;
    rdfs:comment "An actuator in the IoT testbed." ;
    ssn:hasProperty ssn:controls .

iota:Gateway a rdfs:Class ;
    rdfs:label "Gateway" ;
    rdfs:comment "A gateway in the IoT testbed." ;
    ssn:hasProperty ssn:connects .
# ```

# ### Object Properties

# ```turtle
iota:hasDevice a rdf:Property ;
    rdfs:label "has device" ;
    rdfs:comment "A device in the IoT testbed." ;
    rdfs:domain iota:IoTTestbed ;
    rdfs:range iota:Device .

iota:hasNetwork a rdf:Property ;
    rdfs:label "has network" ;
    rdfs:comment "A network in the IoT testbed." ;
    rdfs:domain iota:IoTTestbed ;
    rdfs:range iota:Network .

iota:hasSensor a rdf:Property ;
    rdfs:label "has sensor" ;
    rdfs:comment "A sensor in the IoT testbed." ;
    rdfs:domain iota:IoTTestbed ;
    rdfs:range iota:Sensor .

iota:hasActuator a rdf:Property ;
    rdfs:label "has actuator" ;
    rdfs:comment "An actuator in the IoT testbed." ;
    rdfs:domain iota:IoTTestbed ;
    rdfs:range iota:Actuator .

iota:hasGateway a rdf:Property ;
    rdfs:label "has gateway" ;
    rdfs:comment "A gateway in the IoT testbed." ;
    rdfs:domain iota:IoTTestbed ;
    rdfs:range iota:Gateway .
# ```

# ### Data Properties

# ```turtle
iota:deviceID a rdf:Property ;
    rdfs:label "device ID" ;
    rdfs:comment "The ID of the device." ;
    rdfs:domain iota:Device ;
    rdfs:range rdf:XMLLiteral .

iota:networkID a rdf:Property ;
    rdfs:label "network ID" ;
    rdfs:comment "The ID of the network." ;
    rdfs:domain iota:Network ;
    rdfs:range rdf:XMLLiteral .

iota:sensorID a rdf:Property ;
    rdfs:label "sensor ID" ;
    rdfs:comment "The ID of the sensor." ;
    rdfs:domain iota:Sensor ;
    rdfs:range rdf:XMLLiteral .

iota:actuatorID a rdf:Property ;
    rdfs:label "actuator ID" ;
    rdfs:comment "The ID of the actuator." ;
    rdfs:domain iota:Actuator ;
    rdfs:range rdf:XMLLiteral .

iota:gatewayID a rdf:Property ;
    rdfs:label "gateway ID" ;
    rdfs:comment "The ID of the gateway." ;
    rdfs:domain iota:Gateway ;
    rdfs:range rdf:XMLLiteral .
# ```

# ### Mapping to Fiesta-IOT Ontology

# ```turtle
iota:Device rdfs:subClassOf fiesta:Device .
iota:Network rdfs:subClassOf fiesta:Network .
iota:Sensor rdfs:subClassOf fiesta:Sensor .
iota:Actuator rdfs:subClassOf fiesta:Actuator .
iota:Gateway rdfs:subClassOf fiesta:Gateway .
# # ```

# # ### Mapping to SSN Ontology

# # ```turtle
# iota:Sensor rdfs:subClassOf ssn:Sensor .
# iota:Actuator rdfs:subClassOf ssn:Actuator .
# ```

# This ontology provides a clear and well-defined representation of IoT testbeds, their components, and their relationships. It reuses existing ontologies, vocabularies, and standards whenever possible, ensuring correctness and consistency of reused terms.